Project
-> Gantt Chart(s)
--> Milestones
--> Task Groups
--> Tasks
-> Calendar(s)
--> Events (recurring, all day etc.)
-> Lists
--> sub-lists
--> items

-> People
--> Teams
--> Person

Start with one gantt and one calender per project
create project -> create new chart and new calendar
Milestone - calendar entry, assigned to person/team
Task Group - calender entry, new list, assigned to person/team
Task - list item, assigned

Calendar Event - create new milestone

list -> task
sub-list -> parent becomes task group -> task group added to calendar?
item - nothing

Gantt charts can have split tasks (dotted lines between elements on the same row)